{"tid":2499730,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[FG Offer] Big4 vs Bank MT vs BB","createTime":"2021-04-22T06:06:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T14:42:25.000Z","uid":26666,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"57bc3e3b634d2fcacfef20596b3085b2f221925e","tid":2499730,"uid":26666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:06:12.000Z","msg":"借ac問，21 fg 返緊bank做credit risk modelling，好難得入到行但行頭窄環境太舒服，後生想博殺下，有諗過做跳跳虎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但點都好似唔及先big4後bank咁既path快同人工高。而且有其他offer係手，所以想問下呢幾個offer邊個做career path起點會比較好？唔想開錯個頭...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nCareer path&gt;exposure+exit+錢途<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. Big4 Technology Risk consulting(15.5k)，career path清晰，人工升幅又大，又比錢考cert，跳出去都有啲野揸手咁，自己對tech都有興趣 ，唔介意chur，exposure又大，捱幾年就一條好漢，不過唔肯定tech risk前景好唔好，擔心exit一般<br />\n<br />\n2. 港資中型bank retail MT(~25k)，(未出offer，但考慮埋)好似主要做product/transformation，自己都有興趣，program包升AM，但見有人話過上AM個headcount都要再爭，唔知係咪真。但怕好難轉去大bank，或者轉外資bank，加上見個個都話retail不了，所以有啲猶豫。另外有啲擔心個環境又係好舒服，好穩定咁，後生未想係呢種環境做野住<br />\n<br />\n3. 美資BB IBD Ops Client Onboarding(30k)，perm位，唔係grad program入，名擺cv真係好靚，起薪又高，exposure應該都大，但好似冇exit咁，自己冇諗過轉FO，所以冇所謂，但kyc/aml見比人講到好差咁。自己本身有risk background，就算唔岩自己做，驚拎住個BB名唔會有得轉番去risk，轉做compliance都好似冇乜可能，好似係條dead end黎既咁...<br />\n<br />\n自己都有考慮過移民，雖然未話得埋，但有諗過有big4/BB係cv，好似出國搵工都有些少作用咁。<br />\n<br />\n利申 fg唔太熟行情，如果有理解錯，請隨便指正！Thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勿相認"},{"pid":"ca22d6a81d36c226a4ec1f206bc97bf98873b552","tid":2499730,"uid":113929,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:24:00.000Z","msg":"想移一定係1、3 <br />\nLocal bank 人地鬼聽過個名"},{"pid":"aee1c703e2bddf2a91d90d76e1cd6b173efff981","tid":2499730,"uid":2140,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:25:54.000Z","msg":"3 做得掂轉function 應該唔難<br />\n1 係另一條path<br />\n2 retail 條路應該最明確"},{"pid":"db65d9a800bfbae45875def515868cf487388fc3","tid":2499730,"uid":140018,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:32:01.000Z","msg":"3 la<br />\n大家都係用命換錢，寧願高人工博rotation 好過big4 挨，3唔掂轉1容易，但係1轉3 就好難"},{"pid":"df4958657630c1d7533572299d60ee7573350e37","tid":2499730,"uid":374353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:47:54.000Z","msg":"想問下樓主大學係讀咩方面既科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想了解下你大學做左D咩既準備"},{"pid":"90de905959ff73082b0f2e0dad4758ac997d241a","tid":2499730,"uid":239889,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"db65d9a800bfbae45875def515868cf487388fc3","tid":2499730,"uid":140018,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:32:01.000Z","msg":"3 la<br />\n大家都係用命換錢，寧願高人工博rotation 好過big4 挨，3唔掂轉1容易，但係1轉3 就好難"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T06:58:16.000Z","msg":"Onboarding Ops點轉risk啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 調返轉就易"},{"pid":"22749a21fae9539789a14a22ea4414e81846d557","tid":2499730,"uid":134182,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:07:32.000Z","msg":"梗係3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"113b27174e097eae1e37bf73c6b2d7288cc149b9","tid":2499730,"uid":29121,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:23:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd8211e81ddd0c1df4e3108f10e0c44d22d5e3e8","tid":2499730,"uid":19123,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T07:29:33.000Z","msg":"一定係1<br />\n2同3 依家人工高但其實好冇前途<br />\n你做緊risk modelling 做乜撚野要去做retail bank / Ibank ops <img sr