\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家做左三年 轉左出bank 47k/month +2month bonus<br />\n<br />\n之前有新加坡vb問我去唔去做<br />\n所以如果想移民 1係唔錯選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T08:22:21.000Z","msg":"條path好似唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問之前big4做既project exposure大唔大？<br />\n介唔介意講轉去bank咩位？同埋ching點睇tech risk前景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Thanks"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T10:03:14.000Z","msg":"Big4 好既係可以係短時間做到唔同entity 唔同nature既project, 雖然會忙過一般commercial 但又冇financial audit咁忙 一般7點倒收工 一年有一兩個月忙 可能會收10點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nTech risk有分做technical 同non technical field<br />\nTechnical既會主要做cyber security/ data 個類野<br />\nNon techical 既路 通常會接到it audit/ draft compliance report/ risk assessment 或者incident review 既野黎做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c261e6e13c740d0ef249b713dbe863a69097203","tid":2499730,"uid":67313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T10:17:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}